tests.code:
await driver.get("http://142.93.168.34/account/register")
await driver.findElement(By.css(".op-modal--modal-container > #new_user #user_login")).sendKeys("validUsernameNonExistent")
await driver.findElement(By.css(".op-modal--modal-container > #new_user #user_firstname")).sendKeys("Jenette")
await driver.findElement(By.css(".op-modal--modal-container > #new_user #user_lastname")).sendKeys("Cline")
await driver.findElement(By.css(".op-modal--modal-container > #new_user #user_mail")).sendKeys("existing_email@mailinator.com")

await driver.findElement(By.css(".op-modal--modal-container > #new_user #user_password_confirmation")).sendKeys("password123")
await driver.findElement(By.css(".op-modal--modal-container > #new_user .-highlight")).click()
{
  const elements = await driver.findElements(By.css(".op-modal--modal-container > #new_user > #errorExplanation li"))
  assert(elements.length)
}
assert(await driver.findElement(By.css(".op-modal--modal-container > #new_user > #errorExplanation li")).getText() == "Email has already been taken.")
